@startuml level2_body
!theme plain

title Level 2: Body Domain Architecture\nComfort and Convenience Systems

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor LightPink
    BorderColor DarkRed
    ArrowColor DarkBlue
}

package "Body Domain" {

    component "BCM\n(Body Control Module)" as BCM {
        portin p_door_sensors
        portin p_light_switch
        portin p_ambient_cmd
        portout p_door_status
        portout p_light_control
        portout p_ambient_feedback

        [Door Lock Control]
        [Light Control]
        [Wiper Control]
        [Ambient Light Controller]
    }

    component "DATC\n(Dual Auto Temperature Control)" as DATC {
        portin p_temp_sensors
        portin p_user_setting
        portout p_climate_control

        [Temperature Control]
        [Fan Speed Control]
        [Air Distribution]
    }

    component "FATC\n(Full Auto Temperature Control)" as FATC {
        portin p_temp_sensors
        portin p_user_setting
        portout p_climate_control

        [Auto Climate Control]
        [Zone Control (4 zones)]
        [Air Quality Monitor]
    }

    component "AFLS\n(Adaptive Front Lighting)" as AFLS {
        portin p_steering_angle
        portin p_vehicle_speed
        portout p_light_angle

        [Dynamic Beam Control]
        [Cornering Light]
    }

    component "AHLS\n(Adaptive High-beam Light)" as AHLS {
        portin p_camera_data
        portout p_highbeam_control

        [Auto High Beam]
        [Glare-Free Control]
    }

    component "PSB\n(Pre-Safe Belt)" as PSB {
        portin p_collision_warning
        portout p_belt_tension

        [Belt Pretensioner]
        [Collision Detection]
    }

    component "TPMS\n(Tire Pressure Monitoring)" as TPMS {
        portin p_tire_sensors
        portout p_pressure_warning

        [Pressure Monitoring]
        [Temperature Monitoring]
    }

    component "SMK\n(Smart Key)" as SMK {
        portin p_key_signal
        portout p_auth_status

        [Keyless Entry]
        [Immobilizer]
        [Push Button Start]
    }
}

cloud "CAN-LS\n125 kbps" as CAN3

' BCM Messages
BCM --> CAN3 : **BCM_LightControl (0x520)**\n• Headlight_Status\n• Ambient_Light_Active\n• Ambient_R/G/B_Actual\nCycle: 100ms, QM

CAN3 --> BCM : **IVI_AmbientLight (0x400)**\n• Ambient_Light_RGB\n• Brightness, Theme\n(via Gateway from CAN-HS #2)

BCM --> CAN3 : **BCM_DoorStatus**\n• Door_FL/FR/RL/RR_Open\n• Trunk_Open\nCycle: 100ms

' DATC Messages
DATC --> CAN3 : **DATC11**\n• Target_Temp_Driver/Passenger\n• Fan_Speed\n• Air_Distribution\nCycle: 500ms

' FATC Messages
FATC --> CAN3 : **FATC11**\n• Zone1/2/3/4_Temp\n• Auto_Mode_Active\n• Air_Quality_Index\nCycle: 500ms

' AFLS Messages
AFLS --> CAN3 : **AFLS11**\n• Light_Angle_Left/Right\n• Cornering_Active\nCycle: 100ms

CAN3 --> AFLS : **MDPS12**\n• Steering_Angle\n(via Gateway)

' AHLS Messages
AHLS --> CAN3 : **AHLS11**\n• High_Beam_Active\n• Glare_Free_Mode\nCycle: 100ms

' PSB Messages
PSB --> CAN3 : **PSB11**\n• Belt_Tension_Status\n• Pretensioner_Active\nCycle: 100ms, ASIL-B

CAN3 --> PSB : **ACU_CollisionWarning**\n(via Gateway)

' TPMS Messages
TPMS --> CAN3 : **TPMS11**\n• Tire_Pressure_FL/FR/RL/RR\n• Tire_Temp_FL/FR/RL/RR\n• Warning_Active\nCycle: 1000ms

' SMK Messages
SMK --> CAN3 : **SMK11**\n• Key_Status\n• Auth_Result\n• Immobilizer_Active\nCycle: 100ms

component "CGW\n(Central Gateway)" as CGW
CAN3 --> CGW : Route to CAN-HS #1, #2
CGW --> CAN3 : Vehicle Data, Steering Angle

note right of BCM
  **BCM Key Functions**
  • Door lock/unlock control
  • Exterior/interior lighting
  • Ambient lighting control
  • Wiper control
  • Power window control

  **Safety Level**: QM
  **Cycle Time**: 100ms
  **Feature**: Ambient lighting
end note

note right of TPMS
  **TPMS Key Functions**
  • Tire pressure monitoring
  • Temperature monitoring
  • Low pressure warning
  • Tire position detection

  **Safety Level**: QM
  **Cycle Time**: 1000ms
  **Sensors**: 4 tire sensors
end note

note bottom of CAN3
  **Body CAN Messages**

  Control Messages (100-500ms):
  • BCM_LightControl: Ambient feedback
  • DATC/FATC: Climate control
  • AFLS/AHLS: Lighting control

  Status Messages (1000ms):
  • TPMS: Tire pressure
  • SMK: Key status

  **Total Messages**: ~15 messages
  **ASIL Level**: QM-B
  **Network**: Low-speed (comfort features)
end note

@enduml
